code: export function timeInSeconds(minutes,seconds){return minutes*60+seconds;}export function compareAscend(item1,item2){if(timeInSeconds(item1.minutes,item1.seconds)!=timeInSeconds(item2.minutes,item2.seconds)){return timeInSeconds(item1.minutes,item1.seconds)-timeInSeconds(item2.minutes,item2.seconds);}else{return item1.name.localeCompare(item2.name);}}export function compareDescend(item1,item2){if(timeInSeconds(item1.minutes,item1.seconds)!=timeInSeconds(item2.minutes,item2.seconds)){return timeInSeconds(item2.minutes,item2.seconds)-timeInSeconds(item1.minutes,item1.seconds);}else{return item2.name.localeCompare(item1.name);}}
